f from server to server, but MUCH harder than he makes it sound. Yet another NONLEGENDS Person commmenting on what the server is "really" about. Sorry, just my little rant about dumb people who talk about legends like they have first hand knowlege, even tho it is obvious they dont. Nothing against the Furor personally, never met him, but people like him are just as bad as people who stereotype people and places by "Facts" they <i>think</i> they know.</P><P>Andais Shadowfiend<BR>Warlock<BR>"Life is the maker;<BR>Death ends all.<BR>On broken faith<BR>And faithless thrall<BR>For doom of darkness<BR>Covers all."<BR><img src="http://www.finitesite.com/yenmabek/Necro_Bed.gif" border=0></font></td>

